de.esoco.data

Class SessionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.obrel.core.RelatedObject
      • org.obrel.core.SerializableRelatedObject
        • de.esoco.data.SessionData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.obrel.core.Relatable

    public class SessionData
extends org.obrel.core.SerializableRelatedObject
    A structure that contains data that is associated with a certain session managed by a SessionManager. All session data is stored and accessed as relations.
    See Also:
